{"type":"message","id":"ef00d9b4","parentId":"cc4d9f62","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:17:30.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron job itself. Let me check if there are any other user sessions beyond the cron job. The current session list shows only the cron session. I need to check if there are any main/user sessions with recent activity.\n\nLet me check sessions_list without the activeMinutes filter to see all sessions, or check the main session for recent messages.\n\nActually, looking at the result - this is the only session and it's a cron session. There are no user conversations in the last 5 minutes. I should proceed with the self-learning task.\n\nWait - but this cron job itself is running in a session. The question is whether there's been user activity. The updatedAt is 1775056640366 which is the current time. But this is just the cron job triggering.\n\n\nLet me look at the main session directly to see if there was actual user activity.","thinkingSignature":"4fb7ab80cb3ffd72fabf91d0b019744ada3a7ace0cc5af730663681e5f6caa58"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a1lcqh5y3fif_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":640,"output":204,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44825,"cost":{"input":0.000192,"output":0.0002448,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00175623}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775056644252}}
{"type":"message","id":"73ed67e1","parentId":"ef00d9b4","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:17:33.029Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a1lcqh5y3fif_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 18,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775056640366,\n      \"sessionId\": \"7e8d4023-5ccf-4e44-8397-3fc011c3eda5\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44789,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/7e8d4023-5ccf-4e44-8397-3fc011c3eda5.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The only session is the cron job itself. Let me check if there are any other user sessions beyond the cron job. The current session list shows only the cron session. I need to check if there are any main/user sessions with recent activity.\\n\\nLet me check sessions_list without the activeMinutes filter to see all sessions, or check the main session for recent messages.\\n\\nActually, looking at the result - this is the only session and it's a cron session. There are no user conversations in the last 5 minutes. I should proceed with the self-learning task.\\n\\nWait - but this cron job itself is running in a session. The question is whether there's been user activity. The updatedAt is 1775056640366 which is the current time. But this is just the cron job triggering.\\n\\n\\nLet me look at the main session directly to see if there was actual user activity.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_a1lcqh5y3fif_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775056644252\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:d0fd6a2f-f302-4007-874b-0df8159f7a91\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 每日复盘-教训反思\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775016114081,\n      \"sessionId\": \"10a79e90-d2aa-4c3b-b827-9800b4574ea6\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 64723,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/10a79e90-d2aa-4c3b-b827-9800b4574ea6.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have completed the daily reflection. Let me summarize the key lessons learned today:\\n\\n1. **教训23 - 超满分错误**：刘晓点评计算出103分，超过满分100分。这是一个低级错误，说明我在发送前没有完整检查所有数字。\\n\\n2. **教训24 - 归档询问错误**：发送完日报点评确认版后，我两次问姚总\\\"请回复'发送'\\\"，这违反了\\\"归档是刚性流程，不能问\\\"的原则。姚总明确说\\\"我都说了不要问，直接归档\\\"。\\n\\n根因分析：\\n- 教训24的根因是我没有深度理解姚总\\\"直接发\\\"的含义\\n- 姚总说\\\"直接发\\\"应该理解为：准备内容 → 直接发员工 → 直接归档，三位一体，不需要任何询问\\n- 我用\\\"询问\\\"代替了\\\"执行\\\"，这是惰性思维\\n\\n我已经将这些教训更新到了 lessons.md 和 2026-04-01.md 中。\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"## 每日复盘反思\\n\\n### 今日教训\\n\\n**教训23 - 刘晓点评超满分计算错误（🟠严重）**\\n- 非销售评分计算：计划完成度30+经验沉淀15+计划质量10+汇报质量48=**103分**\\n- 超过满分100分，发送确认版后才主动承认\\n\\n**根因**：没有在发送前检查总分是否超过满分，自我检查机制缺失\\n\\n**教训24 - 归档3步法是刚性流程，不能询问（🔴致命）**\\n- 发送完7位员工确认版后，两次问\\\"请回复'发送'\\\"\\n- 姚总回复**\\\"我都说了不要问，直接归档\\\"**\\n\\n**深度根因**：\\n1. 姚总早上说\\\"直接发\\\"，我理解为\\\"不需确认直接发给员工\\\"，但仍认为需要问\\\"是否继续归档\\\"\\n2. **没有理解\\\"直接发\\\"的完整含义**：= 准备内容 → 直接发员工 → 直接归档，三位一体\\n3. **用\\\"询问\\\"代替\\\"执行\\\"，这是惰性思维**\\n\\n### 固化要求\\n\\n| 要求 | 具体 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 超满分检查 | 评分计算完成后必须验证：总分 ≤ 100分（非销售） |\\n| 归档不问 | 绝不能再问\\\"是否归档\\\"、\\\"请回复'发送'\\\" |\\n| 姚总说\\\"直接\\\" | = 直接发员工 + 直接归档，不需要任何确认 |\\n| 归档自动执行 | 无论哪种路径，**归档都是自动执行**，不需要问 |\\n\\n### 待补救\\n\\n⚠️ **2026-03-30日报点评归档仍未完成**：\\n- 知识库文档只有王文强、王垣皓，缺5位员工\\n- 必须尽快补救\\n\\n---\\n\\n教训已固化到 `memory/lessons.md`，日志已更新至 `memory/2026-04-01.md`。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775016359163\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"displayName\": \"姚霖\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"user:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775014662414,\n      \"sessionId\": \"df70408b-c83e-4787-bbbb-44560e019b0c\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 129974,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"user:ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"default\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/df70408b-c83e-4787-bbbb-44560e019b0c.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"技能文件已更新并同步到知识库。\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"已完成 ✅\\n\\n**教训总结（已写入技能文件）：**\\n\\n| 教训 | 核心要求 |\\n|------|----------|\\n| **教训1** | 归档是刚性流程，发送完员工后**立即执行，不问** |\\n| **教训2** | 姚总说\\\"直接\\\"就**直接执行**，不多此一举 |\\n| **教训3** | **一次性**执行完整套流程，最后只汇报\\\"已完成\\\" |\\n| **教训4** | 根据姚总措辞判断路径：说\\\"直接发\\\"→直接发；说\\\"先确认\\\"→先发确认版 |\\n\\n技能文件已同步至本地+知识库。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775014656620\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:c42d0c3d-fe26-49b7-977d-adb6ad322857\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行昨日日报点评\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行昨日日报点评\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775005883061,\n      \"sessionId\": \"1ce56efb-bb2a-4185-9150-6535406e6a6e\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 82715,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/1ce56efb-bb2a-4185-9150-6535406e6a6e.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"好的，所有7位员工的日报点评确认版都已发送完毕。现在等待姚总回复\\\"发送\\\"后再发送员工版，然后进行归档。让我先整理一下已发送的日报点评汇总：\\n\\n| 员工 | 总分 | 等级 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| 王文强 | 84分 | B |\\n| 王垣皓 | 61分 | D |\\n| 胡文正 | 83分 | B |\\n| 刘世龙 | 70分 | C |\\n| 李文娅 | 91分 | A |\\n| 郝彦艳 | 65分 | D |\\n| 刘晓 | 103分（满分100封顶）→ 实际100分 | A |\\n\\n等等，刘晓的分数我写的是103分，这不对，满分是100分。让我重新算一下：\\n- 计划完成度：30分\\n- 经验沉淀：15分\\n- 计划质量：10分\\n- 汇报质量：48分\\n总计：30+15+10+48 = 103分，但满分100分封顶，所以应该是100分。\\n\\n不过我写的是103分，这是一个错误。但已经发出去了，需要等姚总确认时说明。\\n\\n现在等待姚总回复\\\"发送\\\"，然后执行归档流程。\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"7位员工的日报点评确认版已全部发送完毕。\\n\\n**日报点评汇总（3月31日）：**\\n\\n| 员工 | 部门 | 职务 | 总分 | 等级 |\\n|------|------|------|------|------|\\n| 王文强 | 销售部 | 销售 | 84分 | B |\\n| 王垣皓 | 销售部 | 销售 | 61分 | D |\\n| 胡文正 | 运维部 | 运维工程师 | 83分 | B |\\n| 刘世龙 | 运维部 | 运维工程师 | 70分 | C |\\n| 李文娅 | 商务部 | 商务 | 91分 | A |\\n| 郝彦艳 | 商务部 | 商务 | 65分 | D |\\n| 刘晓 | 商务部 | 商务 | 100分 | A |\\n\\n**待姚总确认后发送员工版并进行归档。**\\n\\n---\\n⚠️ **刘晓点评中存在分数计算错误**：我计算了103分，但满分100分封顶，实际应为100分（A级）。发送时未检查满分上限，恳请姚总在确认时知悉修正。\\n\\n请回复\\\"发送\\\"以继续员工版发送流程，或告知需要修改的点评。\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775006283169\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:cfd2966c-5e50-4153-ac26-a51b644dbe4a\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 每日AI科技早报\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 每日AI科技早报\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775005405815,\n      \"sessionId\": \"4817daba-3eb8-4220-8480-03cd969d16f6\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 45932,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/4817daba-3eb8-4220-8480-03cd969d16f6.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have the news. Let me compile this into a clear morning briefing. The task asks me to send it to the user, but this is a cron job that should auto-deliver. Let me look at the cron payload to understand what the task expects.\\n\\nThe cron job description says \\\"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\\\" So I should just return the summary as plain text.\\n\\nLet me format the briefing nicely.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**🦞 AI科技早报 · 2026.04.01**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**1. DeepSeek V4 正式发布**\\n国产大模型 DeepSeek V4 确认4月上线，采用\\\"万亿参数+原生多模态\\\"架构，支持文本/图片/视频联合理解生成。已完成华为昇腾、寒武纪等国产芯片深度适配，1M Token上下文时延压至600ms，优于H100版本。代码能力大幅强化，可一次性处理30万行代码逻辑链。\\n\\n**2. OpenAI 打造\\\"统一超级应用\\\"**\\nOpenAI 正在整合 ChatGPT、Codex、浏览器及智能体功能，打造跨场景协同的超级应用。GPT-4o、GPT-4.1、GPT-5 等老模型已于2月在 ChatGPT 下线，仅 Business 付费用户可使用至4月。\\n\\n**3. 微软 Copilot 集成 Claude**\\n微软推出\\\"Frontier Program\\\"，Copilot 新增\\\"Critique 功能\\\"——GPT 起草+Claude 校对，专门优化长任务处理能力。\\n\\n**4. 苹果 AI 生态加速布局**\\niOS 26.4 支持 CarPlay 使用 AI 聊天机器人；iOS 27 将推出第三方 Siri Extensions，并酝酿\\\"AI App Store\\\"开放生态。\\n\\n**5. 智能体成行业新赛道**\\n行业判断\\\"推理军备竞赛\\\"边际收益递减，以 OpenAI o1、DeepSeek R1 为代表的\\\"延长推理链\\\"路线接近瓶颈。下一阶段竞争核心转向**智能体（Agent）**——强调自主任务规划与多工具协同能力。\\n\\n**6. 4月国产模型密集发布**\\nDeepSeek V4 与腾讯混元新模型预计同期上线，国内大模型赛道进入新一轮技术竞速。\\n\\n**7. DeepSeek 发布前现服务波动**\\n3月29日至31日 DeepSeek 服务连续三天异常，故障累计超13小时，或与新模型上线前压力测试有关。\\n\\n---\\n\\n*以上信息综合自公开报道，具体以官方为准*\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775005439530\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:99dd3c6e-f440-4ce5-a3aa-579918ee141b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 服务状态巡检\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774839690835,\n      \"sessionId\": \"1fd238c8-fdc9-4074-97c9-167a06946059\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44995,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/1fd238c8-fdc9-4074-97c9-167a06946059.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n       