h 28-29, so the last working day would be March 31 (Tuesday). Since today is only March 30 (Monday), I should respond that today isn't the last working day.\\n\\nThe truncated message at the end likely contains additional instructions for what to do when it is the last working day, but I can't see those details. For now, I'll follow the clear part of the instruction and send the response about today not being the last working day.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**本月最后工作日不是今天，不执行**\\n\\n---\\n\\n**原因**：2026年3月工作日分析：\\n- 3月28日（周六）、3月29日（周日）→ 周末休息\\n- **本月最后工作日为3月31日（周二）**\\n- 今天是3月30日（周一），非本月最后工作日\\n\\n待3月31日再来执行本月日报汇总评价和打分。🦞\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774802419715\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:05e9f9b7-5879-4a26-8345-3d4d0563a347\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本…\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: 请按照日报点评工作流执行本季度的日报汇总评价和打分。首先判断今天是否为本季度最后一个工作日，如果是则执行，否则回复\\\"本…\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774802303001,\n      \"sessionId\": \"32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44170,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/32ae8b6a-6299-422a-91d6-eddffdf330a7.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me think about this. The user is asking me to:\\n1. Check if today (March 30, 2026) is the last working day of this quarter\\n2. If yes, execute the quarterly daily report su